            english=" We've looked up to him for a\nlong time now.",
            french=" On a toujours éprouvé\nle plus grand respect pour lui.",
            german=" Wir sehen schon sehr lange zu\nihm auf.",
            italian=" Provo davvero una grande\nsimpatia per lui.",
